search-filter-clear-selected: Label for button that clears all selected filter values.
search-filter-missing-value: Displayed to indicate a missing field in a toolinfo record.

search-filter-ui-language-value:
Display a language autonym and its ISO 639 language code. Parameters:
* $1 - Language autonym. For example 'English' or 'עברית'.
* $2 - ISO 639 language code. For example 'en' or 'he'.
search-filter-wiki-any: Supported wiki option indicating that the tool can be used with any Wikimedia wiki.

search-filter-wiki-wikinews: Supported wiki option indicating that the tool can be used with any language variant of Wikinews.
search-filter-wiki-wikipedia: Supported wiki option indicating that the tool can be used with any language variant of Wikipedia.

search-filter-wiki-wikiversity: Supported wiki option indicating that the tool can be used with any language variant of Wikiversity.

search-filter-wiki-wiktionary: Supported wiki option indicating that the tool can be used with any language variant of Wikitionary.
